HB4420 HFLR Page 11
BOLD FACE denotes Committee Amendments.

1 read ing intervention plan no later than thirty (30) twenty-one (21)
2 days after the identification of the deficiency in reading. The
3 reading intervention plan shall be provided in addition to core
4 reading instruction that is provided to all students. The reading
