BOLD FACE denotes Committee Amendments.

1 with appropriate training and demonstrated competency
2 in evidence-based reading intervention.
3 L. 1. Beginning with the 2027-2028 school year, third-grade
4 students shall demonstrate sufficient reading skills for promotion
5 to fourth grade. Students shall be provided the following options
6 to demonstrate sufficient reading skills for promotion to fourth
7 grade:
8 a. scoring above the below basic level on the third-grade
9 statewide English Language Arts assessment, or
10 b. earning an acceptable score on an alternative
